Apple-blossom Thrips time series

Source: R/rEDM_package.R
thrips_block.Rd

Seasonal outbreaks of Thrips imaginis.

thrips_block

Format

A data frame with 81 rows and 6 variables:

Year

year

Month

month

Thrips_imaginis

counts of Thrips imaginis

maxT_degC

mean maximum dail temperature in each month (Celsius)

Rain_mm

monthly rainfall (mm)

Season

annual sinusoidal that peaks in December
